510
00:42:41,280 --> 00:42:44,560
Start from 70,000 years ago.

511
00:42:45,740 --> 00:42:49,690
I have always lived in the Early Morning Dawn Palace and don't know about your matters.

512
00:42:49,690 --> 00:42:54,320
I will give you the opportunity now to clarify yourself.

513
00:42:55,600 --> 00:42:57,400
Yes.

